Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After we came to Kaiba Land,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}someone hijacked the dome and trapped us inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we don't defeat the Duel Computer, we'll never get back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The computer's level has been set to its max,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my other self can't even use his own deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but a terrible Dragon Deck that's all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Conspiracy Begins to Move"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't win with that deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah... And the computer he's playing against is set to the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person up there is definitely going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Duel King, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'll lose to a computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, no matter how impossible the situation was, he still overcame it and won!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all Monster Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Petit Dragon in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Defense of only 700...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reverse card face-down either...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no other cards to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reigning Duel King who defeated Seto Kaiba during Battle City...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected him to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is far too amusing to be a mere coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will serve as an entertaining {\i1}vorstellung{\i0} before the curtain drops on my {\i1}true{\i0} performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Herr{\i0} Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plane has been prepared for your flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, {\i1}Herr{\i0} Sieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, {\i1}Herr{\i0} Sieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, {\i1}Herr{\i0} Sieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Activate Magic Card from hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cost Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Discard one card from hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Levels of all Monsters in hand are reduced by two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Angel Knight Perseus can be Summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summon Angel Knight Perseus in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also activate Permanent Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thief Goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Monster inflicts damage to opponent while this card is in play,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you must discard one card from hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Angel Knight Perseus. Attack Petit Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Angel Knight Perseus' Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it attacks Defense Position Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}opponent player receives damage equal to difference in points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, I am permitted to draw one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thief Goblin's Special Effect. Activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please discard card farthest to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Continuing battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Berserk Gorilla. Direct Attack player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless after all, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Yugi hasn't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate continuous effect of Thief Goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please discard the second farthest card to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my turn is then complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because I had such an unbalanced Dragon Deck...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your deck's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the strong feelings these Dragons hold within them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragons' feelings.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in the warm heart of this deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I draw the card my partner put in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Magic Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Sapphire Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, an Equipment Magic from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Dragon's Treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It increases the Attack and Defense of an Equipped Dragon-Type by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sapphire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Angel Knight Perseus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That deck actually had a Magic Card hiding in it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-He did it!\N -That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Killer Snake is in the Graveyard during the Standby Phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can add another to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summon Newt in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's attacking the 2200 Attack Sapphire Dragon with 1900 Attack Newt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the computer broken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Activate Newt's Special Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster destroyed by this Monster in battle has its Attack Power and Defense Power lowered by 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even reducing its own Life Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just to lower its Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, Berserk Gorilla will attack Sapphire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Activate Effect of Permanent Trap, Thief Goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please discard the card farthest to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of something holding the greatest Duelist level of data!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Are we gonna get out of here?\N -H-Hold it, don't grab me like that! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-It'll be all right. Don't worry.\N -What're we supposed to do with you being so negative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making the kids nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-S-Sorry...\N -I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Lurking Dragon in the Cave in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't do anything against 2000 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Sacrifice Berserk Gorilla on field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summon Android - Psycho Shocker in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can even Summon Psycho Shocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just about every well-known Duelist's card data around the entire world exists within that computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Android - Psycho Shocker will attack Lurking Dragon in the Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deck's warm feelings answered you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What card did he get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Baby Dragon in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, from my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Continuous Magic, Willpower of the Ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my key card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ordinary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got a certain {\i1}ring{\i0} to it, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summon Killer Snake in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Android - Psycho Shocker will attack Baby Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Killer Snake. Direct Attack opponent player.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This moment, the effects of the Continuous Magic, Willpower of the Ordinary, will activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the card I draw is a Normal Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I show that card to the opponent and I'm permitted to draw another card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I've drawn is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth-Crawling Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Spirit Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Dragon, attack Android - Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I activate Spirit Dragon's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it battles, for every Dragon-Type Monster I discard to the Graveyard from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its Attack and Defense goes up by 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have six Dragon-Type Monster Cards in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, its Attack goes up by 6000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing to win with that deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, believe in your Monsters and cherish them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick's deck is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna collect Dragon-Types now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would expect nothing less from one who defeated Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh air is really great~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if we'd ever breathe it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! Mama! Something amazing just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be that {\i1}you{\i0} view me as an ordinary "nothing special" guy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Magic Effect is quite handy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}does {\i0}remind me of you a little though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a deadbeat has his use.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU'RE THE LAST ONE I WANNA HEAR THAT FROM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAIBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NOW{\i0} YOU COME!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn Duel Computer you built put us through a lot of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the {\i1}trouble{\i0}, Deadbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone hacked our system from another area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than likely someone who's trying to stop the opening of KC Grand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're using boring tricks to try and stop the revival of Kaiba Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone who challenges me will soon come to regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be on the safe side, run a thorough test on Kaiba Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensure the safety of our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If another disturbance occurs again, they will be displeased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The KC Grand Prix {\i1}must{\i0} be a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all free to do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SO ARROGANT~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without {\i1}us{\i0} here, your tournament won't even {\i1}be{\i0} a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a greatly anticipated Kaiba Corporation Duel Tournament, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to advertise it successfully, we've invited media from all around the globe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, I {\i1}see you{\i0}~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, it's your big brother here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two look like little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} should!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walked right into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Yugi Mutou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} it~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}so{\i0} happy~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to mweet wu~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vivian Wong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}so{\i0} happy to finally meet the legendary Duelist that I dreamed about meeting~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we're rivals in this tournament, in private, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to get along {\i1}very{\i0} well~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell off my Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Chairman Kaiba~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SO COOL~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the KC Grand Prix too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to Duel against you, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do our best when the time comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't all the Duelists arrived yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one left to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualify him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin, Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sieg Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be slightly tardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your invitation, Mr. Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all the Duelists for the tournament are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry to keep you waiting, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba Corporation's prestigious event...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the greatest Dueling Tournament, the KC Grand Prix...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is at last about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Duelists, please come onto the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.39,0:18:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To ensure the greatest challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we have chosen the strongest Duelists from around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First up, we have one who has remained untouchable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who has never lost a tournament up until now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Invincible Boy Prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy was such a famous Duelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mysterious card prophet of destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fortune Salim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His tactics are too smooth for his own good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The drifting Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Edsel Johnson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The assassin from the north...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sergei Ivanov!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And possessing great intellectual properties and observational skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Duelist Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Paul McGregor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the wild gambler...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Abe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will his wild nature overcome the Duels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And performing an open operation even while Dueling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Richard Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the controller of Magic Cards through time itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Magic Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Barry Ginger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, we mean {\i0}this person{\i1} when we speak of magic tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone who Duels while performing using his cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Master of Illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Totani Ialos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who takes all Duels as street fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The road-side fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ethan Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The highly respectful Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jafar Hashin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The beautiful flower of Asia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That person...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vivian Wong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The highly sociable American Champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straight out of the Battle City Best Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Fiery Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} Yeah, Baby~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A.K.A. the ordinary "nothing special" guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since when was I known as "nothing special", huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man whose birthplace and identity is shrouded in mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The legendary Duelist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mask the Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the "Untouchable Emperor of Europe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sieg Lloyd!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And finally, the winner of our previous Battle City Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the Defending Champion, the Duel King will
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}partake in a Duel with the winner of this tournament, betting his title of Duel King on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So only the tournament winner gets to face off against Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duels in this tournament will be decided at random by the main computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't know who you're Dueling until right before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome's the same, whoever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The KC Grand Prix has finally gotten underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Jounouchi will be up fast as he's the first one Dueling in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent he's facing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask the Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that man... no matter how you look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing in this tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, what are you standing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry and get to the playing location...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll run out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jounouchi VS Mask the Rock"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
